    dc:description "Figs 1–2. Euspilotus (Platysaprinus) latimanus (Schmidt, 1890). 1 – habitus, dorsal view; 2 – ditto, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3879850/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5776495>
    dc:description "Figs 23–24. Euspilotus (Platysaprinus) myrmecophilus (Bickhardt, 1910). 23 –habitus, dorsal view (on the photo is the holotype of Saprinus carinipennis Desbordes, 1924); 24 – prosternum, meso- and metaventrite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5776495/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3879858>
    dc:description "Figs 25–33. Male genitalia of Euspilotus (Platysaprinus) myrmecophilus (Bickhardt, 1910). 25 – VIII sternite and tergite, ventral view; 26 – ditto, dorsal view; 27 – ditto, lateral view; 28 – IW and W tergites, dorsal view; 29 – ditto, lateral view; 30 – IW sternite (spiculum gastrale), ventral view; 31 – ditto, lateral view; 32 – aedeagus, dorsal view; 33 – ditto, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3879858/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3879868>
